functions.longDescription:
Compute a CRC16 checksum over a byte buffer.

Workflow examples retained from the previous pack:

```cpp
#include <cstddef>
#include <cstdint>
#include <span>

std::uint16_t Crc16Modbus(std::span<const std::uint8_t> bytes)
{
    std::uint16_t crc = 0xFFFF;
    for (std::uint8_t byte : bytes)
    {
        crc ^= byte;
        for (int bit = 0; bit < 8; ++bit)
        {
            crc = (crc & 1) ? static_cast<std::uint16_t>((crc >> 1) ^ 0xA001)
                            : static_cast<std::uint16_t>(crc >> 1);
        }
    }
    return crc;
}
```

